    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you become the best driver on the Trophy Truck Racing Tour?  Battle against other drivers at several different off-road dirt tracks and experience what it's like to drive one of the most intense off-road trucks ever built.  Master each track and post the best lap time to secure your reputation as one of the best drivers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trophy Truck Racing Tour:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take to the track against a full field of drivers and battle for every position in every corner.  Slide around and try different racing lines to move forward through the field of trucks.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Someone holding you up?  No problem, because these heavy-built trophy trucks can handle a few bumps and scrapes.  Knock your opponents out of the way and test your abilities behind the wheel as you master various off-road tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Trials:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle against the clock and post the best lap time while competing on the Steam Leaderboards.  Every tenth of a second could make a difference as you try to secure your reputation as one of the best drivers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customization:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your Trophy Truck Racing Experience by choosing your number and livery.  Customize the length of your racing sessions and choose from several intense off-road dirt tracks that will test your abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Integration:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controllers and Gamepads are supported for driving controls.  </p>",
